set firefox to not force https:

about:config -> browser.fixup.fallback-to-https -> false

login mariadb:

mysql -u user -p wordpress

SHOW Databases;

USE wordpress;

SHOW tables;

SELECT * FROM wp_comments;

EXIT;


prometheus: hostname/prometheus/graph

up ->running services

100 - (avg by(instance) (rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode="idle"}[5m])) * 100)  -> shows active cpu usage

node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes ->  curent memory usage in bytes

rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total[5m]) -> network acceses in bytes per second 
